Eskom is currently implementing stage 4 of load shedding and this doesn't sit well with Major League. Many South Africans are suffering because of load shedding and have been for a few years now as the power utility battles to keep lights on. The DJ is frustrated because he cannot do his work with load shedding. Taking to his Twitter account, one of the Major twins wrote that load shedding is reducing his productivity. "This load-shedding sh*** is utter rubbish... really and truly. We can’t live like this anymore. We really can’t... literally cutting productivity in half," he wrote. This loadshedding sh*** is utter rubbish.. really and truly. We can’t live like this anymore. We really can’t.. literally cutting productivity in half.  